---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../../styles/globals.css";
import { Header } from "../../components/Header";
import InnerPageCTA from "../../components/InnerPageCTA.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";

const b = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout
  title="Trending Late: The Future of Retail Delivery Predictions - parcelLab"
  description="parcelLab introduces Trending Late, an AI-powered system designed to predict delivery delays early in the shipping process with over 97% accuracy."
>
  <Header client:load />
  <main>
    <section class="section-generous">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1440px] px-6 md:px-12">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px]">
          <a href={`${b}/blog/`} class="group mb-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--ink-muted)] transition-colors hover:text-[#3D3AD3]">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="transition-transform group-hover:-translate-x-0.5"><path d="M19 12H5"/><path d="m12 19-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
            Back to blog
          </a>
          <span class="mb-4 inline-block rounded-full bg-[#3D3AD3]/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-[#3D3AD3]">AI and Analytics</span>
          <h1 class="text-display text-[var(--ink)]">Trending Late: The Future of Retail Delivery Predictions</h1>
          <div class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-[var(--ink-muted)]">
            <span>By <strong class="font-medium text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">Preslav Kisyov</strong></span>
            <span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--ink-muted)]"></span>
            <time datetime="2024-04-03">April 3, 2024</time>
            <span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--ink-muted)]"></span>
            <span>5 min read</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pb-16 md:pb-24">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px] px-6 md:px-12">
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed text-lg">
          Artificial intelligence is proving to be a substantial driver of success in the global economy. Retailers can now leverage AI in inventory and delivery management for data-driven decisions regarding intelligent shipping optimizations and delivery date estimations.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">What is Trending Late?</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          parcelLab has developed Trending Late, an AI system designed to estimate the probability of delivery delays in the post-purchase stage. The predictive machine learning model uses a sophisticated gradient-boosting tree-based algorithm to predict the likelihood of delays throughout the delivery process.
        </p>

        <div class="my-10 rounded-2xl bg-[var(--surface-sunken)] p-8">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-[var(--ink-muted)]">Key Result</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-lg font-medium text-[var(--ink)]">Through rigorous testing, the model demonstrates the potential to predict delays exceptionally early in the shipping process, reaching accuracy scores exceeding 97%.</p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">How This AI Solution Benefits Your Business</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          From a business standpoint, Trending Late reduces the burden on customer support teams by minimizing routine inquiries about order status. The predictive nature enables proactive measurements to prevent customer dissatisfaction. Transparent communication of potential delays establishes trust with customers, pivotal for their retention and loyalty.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <InnerPageCTA />
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
